Description: Automatically generates publication-ready summary tables for descriptive statistics and for comparing binary 
    or three-level groups. Detects variable types (categorical, ordinal, or continuous), 
    applies the appropriate statistical test (Fisher's exact, Chi-squared, Wilcoxon, or Welch t-test), 
    and formats results for export to Word or Excel. Designed for efficient clinical data reporting.
